name: POGO: MARADONA #010
description:
MARADONA #010

“Si me muero quiero volver a nacer y quiero ser futbolista. Y quiero volver a ser Diego Armando Maradona. Soy un jugador que le ha dado alegría a la gente y con eso me basta y me sobra”.

"If I die I want to be born again and I want to be a soccer player. And I want to be Diego Armando Maradona again. I'm a player who has given joy to the people and that's enough for me".


                                                  Diego Armando Maradona (1960-2020)
